text: Oswin Veith (born 1961) is a German politician. Born in Ober-Wöllstadt, Hessen, he represents the CDU. He was a member of the German Bundestag from September 2013 to March 2020. == External links == Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Bundestag for Hesse Category:21st-century German politicians Category:Members of the Bundestag 2017–2021 Category:Members of the Bundestag 2013–2017 Category:Christian Democratic Union of Germany politicians Category:Members of the Bundestag for the Christian Democratic Union of Germany
